
'''Nana Tweneboa Kodua''' yɛ kane ɔman hene wɔ Kumawu a ɔde ne ho bɔɔ afore maa Asantefo nkunimdie. Ɔkomfo anokye de afotuo a ɛnɛ sɛ ansa na Asantefo betumi ade wɔn afiri Denkyirafo nsam wɔ Fahodieko a na ɛrekɔso mu no, gye sɛ ɔde ne ho ma.<ref>http://www.justiceghana.com/index.php/en/2012-01-24-13-47-49/7317-tweneboa-kodua-reincarnated</ref><ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/features/Kumawuman-will-never-again-be-sacrificed-to-appease-or-save-Asantehene-and-or-Asanteman-650141</ref><ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-329-84963-1</ref>

Asantefo no ne Denkyirahene a   ɔde Ntima Gyakari de ɔko sii ani bre bisaa wɔn sɛ wɔnye biribi a ɛhyɛɛ wɔn abufuo no. Nnipa miɛnsa na ɛde wɔn ho bɔɔ afɔree maa asanteman nkunimdie a na Tweneboa Kodua yɛ wɔn mu baako. Odii asrafo no anim kɔɔ ɔko no nanso ɛmfa ho sɛ okura akode ahorɔw pii no, wɔde afutuo maa no sɛ onni ho kwna so ɔto tuo no, Eyi maa wokuu no wɔ ɔko no mu. ɔde abisade too dwa sɛ, ɛnse sɛ wɔde obi a ofiri ne man mu bɔ afɔreɛ biom esiane sɛ w’ayɛ saa ama wɔn nyinaa.<ref>https://afrikanhistory.com/the-reign-of-nana-osei-tutu-i/</ref>

Wɔkyere Ntim Gyakari wɔ Yeyiase na wɔtwaa ne ti. Denkyirafo bɛyɛɛ nkoa maa Asanteman.<ref>http://www.asanteman.org/history-of-the-asante-kingdom--asanteman-.html</ref>

